    "Our node-bit mapping policy ensures that adjacent bins differ by only a single bit pair, which limits the effect of such shifts on the recovered bit sequence.",
    "The tree-based structure enables deterministic computation of these mappings without requiring explicit storage.",
    "Analysis on Distortion and RobustnessThis section presents a theoretical analysis of the distortion and robustness properties of our watermarking scheme, offering insight into its foundational guarantees.",
